owned view sum gives i32:
  let cells be owned buffer of 6 i32 filled with 0
  for each index i of cells:
    cells at i becomes i plus 1
  let middle be view of cells from 2 for 3
  let total be 0
  for each index i of middle:
    total becomes total plus middle at i
  total

main gives i32:
  owned view sum
